21)How to update hive table?
A)By using case when and insert overwrite
insert overwrite table idaa_pipeline. di_amp_subscription_state_dqm_bs_backup1  partition(rt,bt,bsk ) Select 
total_records,total_rules_applied,retry,failed,pass,rule_name,rule_type,product_name,subscription_type,subscription_mode,store_front_id,current_state,platform_name,
case when trim(reporting_date)= '' then NULL else reporting_date end as reporting_date ,etl_process_run_id,rt,bt,bsk from idaa_pipeline. di_amp_subscription_state_dqm_bs  where bsk=114639877

