1)print only even number charecters?
val s = "Hello";
val sb = new StringBuilder();
for (i <- 0 to  s.length) {
if (i%2 == 0 ){
  val c = s.charAt(i);
  print(c)
  }
}
print only odd number charecters?
val s = "Hello"
val sb = new StringBuilder();
for (i <- 0 to  s.length) {
if (i%2 != 0 ){
  val c = s.charAt(i);
  println(c)
  }
}

